{"tid":623521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"父女戀開花結果！石田壹成梅開三度  19歲嫩妻帶球嫁","createTime":"2018-04-10T05:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T08:22:06.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcf24442ccb5366b80c2e32541b6641d5bb8ac6","tid":623521,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"43歲日本男星石田壹成，在90年代曾與福山雅治、酒井法子、江口洋介演出《一個屋簷下》的老三而紅極一時，不過前後2段婚姻及風流情史，都讓他後來遭到冷凍沒有令人印象深刻的代表作品，昨（6）日，他親口證實即將與相差24歲的的舞台劇演員飯村貴子攜手步入第3段婚姻，風流情史完全大勝演藝作品。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/07/1311935-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F1311935-XXL.jpg&h=3dae4bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲▼石田與飯村曾在節目上公開放閃，引起主婦不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/27/1153677-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F1153677-XXL.jpg&h=9c171f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據日媒報導，石田壹成曾表示，想等飯村貴子20歲後再結婚，沒想到日前就傳出閃婚消息，經紀公司也出面證實，2人已入籍，目前同住於月租2.4萬（約台幣6655元）的3坪套房，昨他出席活動時，左手已戴上婚戒，親口透露老婆已懷孕3～4個月，兩人將於下周一登記結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/07/1311942-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F1311942-XXL.jpg&h=3445a424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲石田的風流情史比演藝作品還要精采。<br />\n<br />\n石田去年8月和第二任太太離婚後，無縫和飯村陷入熱戀、同居，這段相差24歲父女戀備受爭議，2人曾上節目放閃，石田壹成自曝，女友洗完澡後，會貼心替對方「擦身體」，27歲的韋碧克相信自己可以在阿仙奴與拿卡錫迪和奧巴美揚爭奪位置，此言論引起主婦觀眾不滿，紛紛打電話至電視台抗議。如今「父女戀」真的修成正果，3度當人夫，再度為人父的石田壹成，昨天出席活動時笑說：「為了即將出世的寶寶，我會努力保養，當個有型的爸爸」。"},{"pid":"9b4a3a64859f63a842807e214c2e85b0dca4244b","tid":623521,"uid":20473,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"睇左石田三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d90f284042eb95385f38fbba5468602106d328","tid":623521,"uid":20522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"韋碧克相信自己可以在阿仙奴與拿卡錫迪和奧巴美揚爭奪位置"},{"pid":"aa92c127424f6e34299331ade2786419e94080ae","tid":623521,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4a3a64859f63a842807e214c2e85b0dca4244b","tid":623521,"uid":20473,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"睇左石田三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ca4d6e9800de6c9d10c3bf3e974e5a4911c225","tid":623521,"uid":78131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7d90f284042eb95385f38fbba5468602106d328","tid":623521,"uid":20522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"韋碧克相信自己可以在阿仙奴與拿卡錫迪和奧巴美揚爭奪位置"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"In wenger we trust"},{"pid":"3d19cd6a612365eb9f1a4fa28c63a7a981807c7e","tid":623521,"uid":131563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"就禿"},{"pid":"649b20f3742da44e2c8b3f7c022df47c4e42b0fc","tid":623521,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"和也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前勁鍾意佢，而家搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe46153ff98ff6b27c5a7c07eb863170dd7a81b9","tid":623521,"uid":91604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"目前同住於月租2.4萬（約台幣6655元）的3坪套房，<br />\n咁平?"},{"pid":"15e40ab30b45f790fc9c789e84583eebaff18062","tid":623521,"uid":162158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe46153ff98ff6b27c5a7c07eb863170dd7a81b9","tid":623521,"uid":91604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"目前同住於月租2.4萬（約台幣6655元）的3坪套房，<br />\n咁平?"},"citedBy":0,"reply